    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMoon_rough.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638169/RenderMoon_rough.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432700705&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638169/RenderMoon_rough.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432700705&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638209\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMoon_rough.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638169\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"53aeb30a-445f-4e86-aa11-361aff148025\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638169/RenderMoon_rough.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432700705&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=854 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638169/RenderMoon_rough.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432700705&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427 1x\"></span><p>The point or particle primitive is intended to be used for tiny objects such as sparks, snowflakes, or raindrops. They are optimized for the case where the intended particle takes up only a couple of pixels on the screen.</p><p>RfB supports Blender’s particle systems, including instancing, a very common use for particles.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_Particles_1.JPG\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638169/RenderMan_Particles_1.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432700705&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=365\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638169/RenderMan_Particles_1.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432700705&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1147\" data-width=\"2384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638212\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Particles_1.JPG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638169\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"4a7be2e0-2aeb-4c41-a7de-82266e3d1221\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638169/RenderMan_Particles_1.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432700705&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=730 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638169/RenderMan_Particles_1.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432700705&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=365 1x\"></span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"4aa610cc-7e6a-4a1b-b5e6-47ba1c998acc\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>For the Halo type, we render the particle system as RiPoints. </p></div></div><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"356b2a47-fde5-4ab1-a879-12f61a5c0c28\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>Note, motion blur is done via the velocity vector.</p></div></div><p /><h3 id=\"Particles-Visibility\">Visibility</h3><p>There are also many times that you want to render the particles without rendering the emitter geometry.  The best way to achieve this with RfB is to turn off Camera Visibility (there are also times when you’ll want to turn off Indirect &amp; Transmission Visibility too)</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_Particles_2.JPG\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638169/RenderMan_Particles_2.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432700481&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=300\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638169/RenderMan_Particles_2.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432700481&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1257\" data-width=\"3182\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638206\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Particles_2.JPG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638169\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"1f2dbd05-07cb-4292-b95d-bb9046333877\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638169/RenderMan_Particles_2.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432700481&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=600 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638169/RenderMan_Particles_2.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432700481&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=300 1x\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_Particles_4.JPG\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638169/RenderMan_Particles_4.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432700481&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=366\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638169/RenderMan_Particles_4.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432700481&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"557\" data-width=\"1156\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638203\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Particles_4.JPG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638169\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"15f8c993-c950-40fe-9795-0cd70412f4cf\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638169/RenderMan_Particles_4.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432700481&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1156&amp;height=557 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638169/RenderMan_Particles_4.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432700481&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=366 1x\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_Particles_3.JPG\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638169/RenderMan_Particles_3.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432700480&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=302\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638169/RenderMan_Particles_3.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432700480&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1263\" data-width=\"3178\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638200\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Particles_3.JPG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638169\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"b5e91046-88e1-48a3-b217-de40d26bfa9d\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638169/RenderMan_Particles_3.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432700480&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=604 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638169/RenderMan_Particles_3.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432700480&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=302 1x\"></span><p />"
